<Layout title="Wedding Invitation Suites | Editable Wedding Invitation Templates" description="Browse editable wedding invitation suites with matching RSVP cards, detail cards, menu cards, and printable wedding stationery templates.">
  <main>
    <section class="page-hero"><div class="container content"><p class="eyebrow">Wedding invitation suites</p><h1>Editable wedding invitation suites for a polished celebration.</h1><p class="lead">Find coordinated wedding invitation suites designed to make your stationery feel cohesive, beautiful, and easy to customize.</p></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container content"><h2>What is included in a wedding invitation suite?</h2><p>A wedding invitation suite usually includes the main invitation, RSVP card, details card, and optional matching pieces like menu cards, thank you cards, programs, and wedding signs.</p><ul class="list"><li>Main wedding invitation template</li><li>RSVP card template</li><li>Details card template</li><li>Optional menu cards, thank you cards, and signage</li><li>Editable files for easy customization</li></ul></div></section>
    <section class="section"><div class="container"><p class="eyebrow">Shop by style</p><h2>Popular wedding invitation suite styles</h2><div class="grid"><div class="card"><h3>Minimalist Wedding Invitation Suites</h3><p>Simple, modern layouts with clean typography and timeless details.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Mid-Century Wedding Invitation Suites</h3><p>Warm colors, retro shapes, and playful design details for stylish couples.</p></div><div class="card"><h3>Elegant Wedding Invitation Suites</h3><p>Refined invitation sets with a polished look for formal and semi-formal weddings.</p></div></div></div></section>
